parameters.parameter: Welcome to the O R D E R platform!

This site is built on the platform titled "O R D E R" (as in the opposite of disorder).

Designers: Victor Brodsky, Oleg Ivanov

Developer: Oleg Ivanov

Quality Assurance Testers: Oleg Ivanov, Steven Bowe, Emilio Madrigal

We are continuing to improve this software. If you have a suggestion or believe you have encountered an issue, please don't hesitate to email slidescan@med.cornell.edu and attach relevant screenshots.


O R D E R is made possible by:


  • PHP

  • Symfony

  • Doctrine

  • MSDN library: ldap_bind_s

  • SwiftmailerBundle

  • AsseticBundle

  • FOSUserBundle

  • PHP Excel

  • OneupUploaderBundle

  • Dropzone JS

  • jsTree

  • KnpPaginatorBundle

  • Twig

  • Bootstrap

  • JS promises Q

  • jQuery

  • jQuery UI

  • jQuery Inputmask

  • Select2

  • Bootstrap Datepicker

  • Bootstrap DateTime Picker

  • Typeahead with Bloodhound

  • Image Cropper

  • Handsontable

  • KnpSnappyBundle with wkhtmltopdf

  • LibreOffice

  • PDFMerger

  • Password Generator

  • Password Encoder

  • jQuery FullCalendar bundle

  • PNotify JavaScript notifications
